{"tid":1190383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛出來了！！！","createTime":"2019-06-07T09:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T23:16:15.000Z","uid":50457,"like":88,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a84a7d540104adf02115cc53f7e5a03825e93b","tid":1190383,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"同選舉臨近勁似，一大堆post主要想挑釁討論區參選者的情緒，既無內容，也沒有意義。<br />\n<br />\n佢地一窩峰就住一兩件小事洗版，瘋狂開同一類型的post, 以阻止其他正常的話題於第一版出現。<br />\n<br />\n6月4日前出現<br />\n1. 遊行示威集會無用論 （返工不了）<br />\n2. 集會只是籌款論 （捐錢不了）<br />\n<br />\n6月4日後開始出現<br />\n<br />\n1. 名人表態論 （標籤化）<br />\n2. 服飾顏色論 （群眾分化）<br />\n3. 割蓆與否論 （醜化）<br />\n<br />\n好快會出現<br />\n1. 捉內鬼猜疑（茅頭實會指向遊行發起人）<br />\n2. 阻人升級論<br />\n3. 升級失敗論<br />\n<br />\n以上種種莫過於達到以下目的：<br />\n1. 自我放棄 （矮化群眾力量）<br />\n2. 互相指責 （打散群眾力量）<br />\n3. 武力恐嚇 （防止群眾力量凝聚）<br />\n<br />\n作為成年人，遊行係表達自己對政府暴政睇法的合法方式。無人叫你捐錢，亦無人攞把槍指住你參與，更加唔會有人因為你著唔同色的衫而趕你走。<br />\n<br />\n每個人都是獨立的個體，有自己的思想，如果你本心一橫留係屋企食花生無問題，同樣你參與遊行，甚至絕食等都係你的選擇，無人阻到你。<br />\n<br />\n對於假膠，五毛，對唔住你的歪論對香港人是無用的。"},{"pid":"d9059ea02db36875dc8ee3183c359aa6f6c0fb18","tid":1190383,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c400e67cd9d5460a459373745fafa95e753a26e","tid":1190383,"uid":229609,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:38:58.000Z","msg":"因為質素關係,佢地既人工已經由5毛減到3毛。<br />\n<br />\n所以宜家d 5毛真係連5毛都不如嫁......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce340a81ea9478afada2587ca38c5f7be8cfd917","tid":1190383,"uid":216477,"like":8,"dislike":19,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57ddca71dadbd40baaf22e62c882ca55de44fd0b","tid":1190383,"uid":233593,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:45:23.000Z","msg":"太多字無睇晒<br />\n我都覺得無必要為同一個議題開咁多post<br />\n手法有啲低裝"},{"pid":"bc78e09db7d2283a1bfeef0e85efe0e20b4b6600","tid":1190383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc23e934a6b7efff80e6976f19f72deeab3bddb","tid":1190383,"uid":40628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55db3968374a4646fd223e83e3a67b74fbccf2ce","tid":1190383,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"6月9號星期日見"},{"pid":"58fd4b5d6bcebbd7c7ca2a7c3dd6def76265df54","tid":1190383,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:47:40.000Z","msg":"高級五毛出動"},{"pid":"186d3c4318f1da9b3a66ca78ead2fc9d92b0ce34","tid":1190383,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"411c7a937009948d3477773f4c28b00e887836ba","tid":1190383,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c400e67cd9d5460a459373745fafa95e753a26e","tid":1190383,"uid":229609,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:38:58.000Z","msg":"因為質素關係,佢地既人工已經由5毛減到3毛。<br />\n<br />\n所以宜家d 5毛真係連5毛都不如嫁......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"唔使幾耐會由3毛減到1毛<br />\nTencent! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b91286b3a49be62e2df5ab17d1b50a7153fcae8","tid":1190383,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:26:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebf378f9e8129454d3fa8725605226be91aa7faa","tid":1190383,"uid":50457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T22:27:03.000Z","msg":"開始一堆假膠post， fake news 洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目的都只是一樣，令群眾力量減少"},{"pid":"ff2dbe281410a4581a210b9d9f38befa04f895d4","tid":1190383,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ebf378f9e8129454d3fa8725605226be91aa7faa","tid":1190383,"uid":50457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T22:27:03.000Z","msg":"開始一堆假膠post， fake news 洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目的都只是一樣，令群眾力量減少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T22:36:40.000Z","msg":"好多人話單野得連登仔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa236c4af5cd06af4a7798c2f2fee19415b15b0","tid":1190383,"uid":226955,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T23:04:52.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例之三毛對答指南：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.）香港人咩都唔做<br />\n答：死港燦咪又係靠中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇中國你地咩都唔係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.）香港人開始反抗<br />\n答：你班港喱咪又係鳩嗡吓，唔係以為真係可以推倒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.）香港人開街站宣傳反修例<br />\n答：成班毛都未生齊嘅撚樣咪喺度精神勝利法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你以為你地好型呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.）香港人聯署白宮<br />\n答：見到班連登仔以為聯署白宮以為有用喎，收皮啦！好撚柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.）香港人6月9號去遊行<br />\n<br />\n答1：諗住打咭上ig fb刷存在感？死返你個乞衣屋企啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />沖涼然後縮入你張碌架床訓覺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n答2：即使比你再嚟多次50萬人行就有用咩？咪又係唱下歌之後第二日照常返工！<br />\n<br />\n答3：今天我/ 要返工不了/做政客嘅爛頭卒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/ 之前連登仔又話焦土？係焦土就咪遊行啦<br />\n<br />\n答4：泛民割席呀！成班柒頭比人利用曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要比人話佢係三毛：<br />\n1.）講真話都比人話係三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.）死柒頭咪係到屈毛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.）一有人講異見說話就屈毛，連登仔惡撚過共產黨紅衛兵呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多不能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6c7f9f47664bb5b2a3b4746566e0f68aa5350a","tid":1190383,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T23:08:03.000Z","msg":"樓主，每逢大遊行前推返呢個post"},{"pid":"41f074ced6a94554bff7d1dc1af096894aadb2c3","tid":1190383,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T23:42:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"734cca8346ac07022547c3b09dfcbf1371c60d9a","tid":1190383,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:17:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80517118b78aa72fe059e484c66ea0adf29fba3a","tid":1190383,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fc3051e879dbac2cecde75b2db5f85df3e0ae6","tid":1190383,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9d0fd2c1167bac5889df3b914e6a89bf728fdd","tid":1190383,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2edb